{"id":774,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":774,"title":"Jeremiah 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Judgments will be poured out upon the people of Judah because of their sins—Their iniquities cause blessings to be withheld from them."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.1","order":"02.25.005.50997"},["b","1"],"Run ye to and fro through the streets of Jerusalem, and see now, and know, and seek in the broad places thereof, if ye can find a man, if there be",["i","any"],"that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"executeth judgment"],", that seeketh the truth; and I will pardon it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.2","order":"02.25.005.50998"},["b","2"],"And though they say, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"liveth; surely they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"swear"],"falsely."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.3","order":"02.25.005.50999"},["b","3"],"O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","are"],"not thine eyes upon the truth? thou hast stricken them, but they have not grieved; thou hast consumed them,",["i","but"],"they have refused to receive correction: they have made their faces harder than a rock; they have refused to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"return"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.4","order":"02.25.005.51000"},["b","4"],"Therefore I said, Surely these",["i","are"],"poor; they are foolish: for they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"know not"],"the way of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","nor"],"the judgment of their God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.5","order":"02.25.005.51001"},["b","5"],"I will get me unto the great men, and will speak unto them; for they have known the way of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","and"],"the judgment of their God: but these have altogether broken the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"yoke"],",",["i","and"],"burst the bonds."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.6","order":"02.25.005.51002"},["b","6"],"Wherefore a lion out of the forest shall slay them,",["i","and"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"wolf"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"evenings"],"shall spoil them, a leopard shall watch over their cities: every one that goeth out thence shall be torn in pieces: because their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"transgressions"],"are many,",["i","and"],"their backslidings are increased."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.7","order":"02.25.005.51003"},["b","7"],"¶How shall I pardon thee for this? thy children have forsaken me, and sworn by",["i","them that are"],"no gods: when I had fed them to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"full"],", they then committed",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"adultery"],", and assembled themselves by troops in the harlots’ houses."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.8","order":"02.25.005.51004"},["b","8"],"They were",["i","as"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fed horses"],"in the morning: every one neighed after his neighbour’s wife."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.9","order":"02.25.005.51005"},["b","9"],"Shall I not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"visit"],"for these",["i","things?"],"saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": and shall not my soul be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"avenged"],"on such a nation as this?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.10","order":"02.25.005.51006"},["b","10"],"¶Go ye up upon her walls, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"destroy"],"; but make not a full",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"end"],": take away her battlements; for they",["i","are"],"not the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.11","order":"02.25.005.51007"},["b","11"],"For the house of Israel and the house of Judah have dealt very treacherously against me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.12","order":"02.25.005.51008"},["b","12"],"They have belied the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and said,",["i","It is"],"not he; neither shall evil come upon us; neither shall we see",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sword"],"nor famine:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.13","order":"02.25.005.51009"},["b","13"],"And the prophets shall become wind, and the word",["i","is"],"not in them: thus shall it be done unto them."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.14","order":"02.25.005.51010"},["b","14"],"Wherefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of hosts, Because ye speak this word, behold, I will make my words in thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"mouth"],"fire, and this people wood, and it shall devour them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.15","order":"02.25.005.51011"},["b","15"],"Lo, I will bring a nation upon you from far, O house of Israel, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": it",["i","is"],"a mighty nation, it",["i","is"],"an ancient nation, a nation whose",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"language"],"thou knowest not, neither understandest what they say."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.16","order":"02.25.005.51012"},["b","16"],"Their quiver",["i","is"],"as an open sepulchre, they",["i","are"],"all mighty men."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.17","order":"02.25.005.51013"},["b","17"],"And they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"eat"],"up thine harvest, and thy bread,",["i","which"],"thy sons and thy daughters should eat: they shall eat up thy flocks and thine herds: they shall eat up thy vines and thy fig trees: they shall impoverish thy fenced cities, wherein thou trustedst, with the sword."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.18","order":"02.25.005.51014"},["b","18"],"Nevertheless in those days, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I will not make a full end with you."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.19","order":"02.25.005.51015"},["b","19"],"¶And it shall come to pass, when ye shall say, Wherefore doeth the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God all these",["i","things"],"unto us? then shalt thou answer them, Like as ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"forsaken"],"me, and served strange",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"gods"],"in your land, so shall ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"serve"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"strangers"],"in a land",["i","that is"],"not yours."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.20","order":"02.25.005.51016"},["b","20"],"Declare this in the house of Jacob, and publish it in Judah, saying,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.21","order":"02.25.005.51017"},["b","21"],"Hear now this, O",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"foolish"],"people, and without understanding; which have eyes, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"see not"],"; which have ears, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"hear"],"not:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.22","order":"02.25.005.51018"},["b","22"],"Fear ye not me? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": will ye not tremble at my presence, which have placed the sand",["i","for"],"the bound of the sea by a perpetual decree, that it cannot pass it: and though the waves thereof toss themselves, yet can they not prevail; though they roar, yet can they not pass over it?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.23","order":"02.25.005.51019"},["b","23"],"But this people hath a revolting and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"rebellious"],"heart; they are revolted and gone."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.24","order":"02.25.005.51020"},["b","24"],"Neither say they in their heart, Let us now fear the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God, that giveth rain, both",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"the"],"former and the latter, in his season: he reserveth unto us the appointed weeks of the harvest."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.25","order":"02.25.005.51021"},["b","25"],"¶Your iniquities have turned away these",["i","things,"],"and your sins have withholden good",["i","things"],"from you."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.26","order":"02.25.005.51022"},["b","26"],"For among my people are found",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"wicked"],["i","men:"],"they lay wait, as he that setteth snares; they set a trap, they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"catch"],"men."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.27","order":"02.25.005.51023"},["b","27"],"As a cage is full of birds, so",["i","are"],"their houses full of deceit: therefore they are become",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"great"],", and waxen rich."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.28","order":"02.25.005.51024"},["b","28"],"They are waxen fat, they shine: yea, they overpass the deeds of the wicked: they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"judge not"],"the cause, the cause of the fatherless, yet they prosper; and the right of the needy do they not judge."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.29","order":"02.25.005.51025"},["b","29"],"Shall I not visit for these",["i","things?"],"saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": shall not my soul be avenged on such a nation as this?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.30","order":"02.25.005.51026"},["b","30"],"¶A wonderful and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"horrible"],"thing is committed in the land;"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31","order":"02.25.005.51027"},["b","31"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"prophets"],"prophesy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"falsely"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"priests"],"bear rule by their means; and my people",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_31d"},"love"],["i","to have it"],"so: and what will ye do in the end thereof?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.1a","order":"02.25.005.51028"},["b","1a"],["span.small","OR"],"does justly.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.26"},"Gen. 18:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.30"},"Ezek. 22:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.2a","order":"02.25.005.51030"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/swearing"},"TG Swearing"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.3a","order":"02.25.005.51032"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"repent.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17"},"Hag. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.4a","order":"02.25.005.51034"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ignorance"},"TG Ignorance"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.5a","order":"02.25.005.51036"},["b","5a"],["span.small","IE"],"of the law and the covenants."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.6a","order":"02.25.005.51038"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.3"},"Zeph. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.6b","order":"02.25.005.51040"},["b","6b"],["span.small","OR"],"plains, wilderness."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.6c","order":"02.25.005.51042"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.7a","order":"02.25.005.51044"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.15"},"Deut. 32:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.7b","order":"02.25.005.51046"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.8a","order":"02.25.005.51048"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"lusty stallions."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.9a","order":"02.25.005.51050"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"punish (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.29"},"v. 29"],")."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.9b","order":"02.25.005.51052"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.9"},"Jer. 9:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.22"},"44:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.10a","order":"02.25.005.51054"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/39.8.8-10"},"Jer. 39:8 (8–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.10b","order":"02.25.005.51056"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.27"},"Jer. 4:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.12a","order":"02.25.005.51058"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.13"},"Jer. 14:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.14a","order":"02.25.005.51060"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.15a","order":"02.25.005.51062"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/33.19"},"Isa. 33:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.17a","order":"02.25.005.51064"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.51.31,33,51"},"Deut. 28:51 (31, 33, 51)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.19a","order":"02.25.005.51066"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.19b","order":"02.25.005.51068"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.19c","order":"02.25.005.51070"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.19d","order":"02.25.005.51072"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.21a","order":"02.25.005.51074"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/foolishness"},"TG Foolishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.21b","order":"02.25.005.51076"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.21c","order":"02.25.005.51078"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.14"},"Matt. 13:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.23a","order":"02.25.005.51080"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.8"},"Ps. 78:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.24a","order":"02.25.005.51082"},["b","24a"],["span.small","IE"],"winter and spring."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.26a","order":"02.25.005.51084"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.26b","order":"02.25.005.51086"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.13"},"D&C 10:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.27a","order":"02.25.005.51088"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"TG Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.28a","order":"02.25.005.51090"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"TG Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.30a","order":"02.25.005.51092"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/6.10"},"Hosea 6:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31a","order":"02.25.005.51094"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31b","order":"02.25.005.51096"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.8"},"Jer. 7:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.13"},"Lam. 4:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31c","order":"02.25.005.51098"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priestcraft"},"TG Priestcraft"],"."],["div",{"id":"31d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31d","order":"02.25.005.51100"},["b","31d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.32"},"Rom. 1:32"],"."]]}
